  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large paella pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add onion and garlic and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add asparagus and cook until tender.",
    "Add smoked paprika, saffron, salt, black pepper, and red pepper flakes. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add chicken broth and bring to a simmer.",
    "Add Spanish rice and stir to combine.",
    "Cook for 20 minutes, or until the rice is tender and the liquid has been absorbed.",
    "Top with Parmesan cheese and serve."
